  "commit_message": "feat(ui): Pro-only hint on Slack/Teams catalog cards pointing at Notifications\n\nAfter the OrgIntegrations Catalog redesign and the notifications framework\nlanding in rearm-core (PR #184), Pro users have two surfaces that both list\n\"Slack\" and \"MS Teams\" as destinations: the legacy IntegrationService cards\nshown here, and the new NotificationChannel framework managed under\nNotifications. The destination is the Slack webhook URL, not the workspace,\nso per-concern channels with separate webhooks is",
